@prefix rdfs: <http://www.w3.org/2000/01/rdf-schema#> .
@prefix sc: <https://schema.software-metadata.pub/software-card/2025-01-01/#> .
@prefix scex: <https://schema.software-metadata.pub/software-card/2025-01-01/examples/#> .
